ts/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d1c6bf4346eefa52ee0cb732fd0015bd6f750e","tid":215582,"uid":266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:08:02.000Z","msg":"呢隻膠環用左半個月都無就黃晒啦"},{"pid":"f4eaefc626e8ad340f4c645162a1d41ee547132f","tid":215582,"uid":81508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:20:06.000Z","msg":"屌次次見到都屌左聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 柒撚到咁都照用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e4a7c5878e896c8fc3a5e761f14f6cb05708a4","tid":215582,"uid":12252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:24:02.000Z","msg":"正常都唔會掂啦"},{"pid":"9746b48e6e4e873e76eadc63b15d6e774ba58570","tid":215582,"uid":51584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:24:14.000Z","msg":"難揸到on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ca5c824759d8443e24535cbe4ec51f80a5dd7a","tid":215582,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:27:04.000Z","msg":"又可以買過批了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a87c21fcde8e881061a79f9a29f871a6adc143a","tid":215582,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:30:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b04a7c98184342c9ed9f8532dfb40b9f67228e43","tid":215582,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:35:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雲海fb: <br />\n<br />\n其實想講講，這兩三個星期我在處理港鐵新扶手問題。其實原本我一點也不覺得有出錯！是朋友的老師託人找我去反映問題，原來南港島線、馬鞍山線，車廂內扶手對於好多殘障人士是相當不受力，而他們曾經向港鐵反映，但得到hea回覆！ok, 我來吧！而我亦都親身去嘗試使用這些膠帶扶手！發現除了新線，舊線原來也新扶手，發現原來確實頗難受力！亦都可以聯想到，若果是老人家持拐杖、孕婦等用這些新扶手是有點問題，也會出現安全隱患！於是乎我就致電港鐵問清楚發生乜事，最初港鐵同我講話新扶手係有專門嘅團隊同事係負責設